Quickstrike:





Quickstrike looked around the room behind the vent. He watched the door, 
just waiting for it to open, but nothing happened. "Looks like it's all 
clear lil' lady."

He thrusted his claws forward, knocking the vent face out. He looked down 
and crawled down the wall. He didn't have to jump due to the helpful barbs 
at the bottom of his walking legs. He looked back up at Dark Mouse.

He transformed to robot mode. "Ya need help gettin' down?"
